# Keep the repro build context tiny and hermetic. The build needs only source +
# lockfiles; host build artifacts must never enter the image (they bloat the COPY
# — `target/` alone is tens of GB — and risk cargo reusing host-built objects
# instead of compiling fresh, which would break reproducibility).
#
# The frontend's dist/ is rebuilt inside the container and copied from the frontend
# stage, so the host copy is excluded too.

/target
/out
/release
.git
**/node_modules
frontend/dist
frontend/.svelte-kit
**/*.tmp
